# Cloudflare Pages headers — 安全強化 + cache 控制（新工具 starter 範本）
# 複製到新 repo 根目錄。把 <TODO-WORKER-URL> 換成本工具自己的 worker（沒有後端就刪掉該段）。
# CSP 已放行 portal CDN 全 src（fat-cat / header / settings 等資產）+ CF Web Analytics。
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/headers/

/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=(), payment=()
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://ffxiv-tw-tools-portal.pages.dev https://static.cloudflareinsights.com; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://ffxiv-tw-tools-portal.pages.dev; img-src 'self' data: https://ffxiv-tw-tools-portal.pages.dev; connect-src 'self' https://ffxiv-tw-tools-settings-api.ffxiv-tw-tools.workers.dev https://cloudflareinsights.com <TODO-WORKER-URL>; media-src 'self' https://ffxiv-tw-tools-portal.pages.dev; font-src 'self' https://ffxiv-tw-tools-portal.pages.dev data:; frame-ancestors 'none'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'none'

# 工具自家 JS / CSS — max-age=0 + must-revalidate → push 完 F5 即時更新（免 Ctrl+Shift+R）
/*.js
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate
/*.css
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate

# HTML 入口 — 永遠跟 server 重驗證
/
  Cache-Control: no-cache
/index.html
  Cache-Control: no-cache
